{"TopicId":94993,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Manoeuvre nodes","CreatedByName":"jonnyb","CreatedById":133815,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-12-30T11:34:27Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"jonnyb","CreatedById":133815,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-12-30T11:34:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EFor some reason I am unable to create manoeuvre nodes. When I try to click on my orbit nothing happens and my orbit is in grey.I am using windows 7 operating system and the ksp version is 90 beta.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"vexx32","CreatedById":12283,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-12-30T12:49:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYou\u0027ll need to upgrade the Tracking Station and the Mission Control buildings at least once before you gain the ability to use manoeuvre nodes in Career mode as of 0.90. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jonnyb","CreatedById":133815,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-12-30T13:34:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ehow do you do this?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"UmbralRaptor","CreatedById":2767,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-12-30T19:43:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jonnyb\u0022 data-cite=\u0022jonnyb\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003Ehow do you do this?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFrom the space center view, right click on a building to bring up the upgrade dialog.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jonnyb","CreatedById":133815,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-12-30T22:36:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThankyou very much\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}